  "id": "RAW_2b338f",
  "title": "R1 怎么落地，看看这 100+ 接入 DeepSeek 的应用是怎么做的？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/woZXLgOGyroRppQjGjGJow",
  "date": "2025-02-14 11:26:32",
  "author": "程 茜",
  "siteName": "Founder Park",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></p>\n  <section>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n    <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\">R1&nbsp;发布后，</span><span style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">据智东西统计（</span><span style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 14px;\">截至 2月 12 日</span><span style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">），目前已经有上百个应用接入DeepSeek模型。</span>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">仅是DeepSeek官方整理的“DeepSeek实用集成”名单，就有54款接入DeepSeek的应用，包括24个应用程序、3个AI Agent框架、1个RAG框架、1个Solana框架、3个即时通讯插件、8个浏览器插件、2个VS Code插件、3个neovim插件、2个JetBrains插件等。</span><span style=\"font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"></span></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\">除了这份清单外，近期国内企业密集宣布旗下软件接入DeepSeek。经智东西统计，至少有57款应用已集成DeepSeek，涵盖金融、教育、医疗、办公、智能助手、娱乐购物等场景，涉及百度、昆仑万维、出门问问、知乎、360、秘塔AI、QQ音乐以及7家手机厂商、数十家基金、证券公司等企业。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\">这些应用根据自己的功能属性，选择了集成满血版DeepSeek推理模型或基于其开源的蒸馏小模型等，所以用户体验到的DeepSeek能力会存在明显差异。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\">以下是超100款DeepSeek应用合集：</span></section><ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;padding-left:1.5em;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n  </ul>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\"></span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <strong style=\"color: rgb(75, 110, 245);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 36px;\">01&nbsp;</span></strong>\n  </section>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 20px;\">54个集成应用Tips</span></strong></h2>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\">去年1月11日，DeepSeek开源了国内首个MoE大模型DeepSeekMoE，并同步在GitHub主页整理了一份“DeepSeek实用集成”清单。</span></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\">应用程序的名单中，有支持大语言模型部署在桌面客户端、在微信上用DeepSeek管理笔记、移动端的AI助手、辅助论文阅读、词典翻译、视频生成等类型的应用。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\">与DeepSeek集成的框架可以简化开发者的开发流程，基于已集成的开源框架快速调用，即时通讯等插件，使得用户可以基于其一键将DeepSeek的相应能力集成至微信、飞书、企业微信、浏览器中。</span></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"2398\" data-ratio=\"4.266666666666667\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/95de91cd-c2e7-4b2b-34c5-42111e316a00/public\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/95de91cd-c2e7-4b2b-34c5-42111e316a00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">▲DeepSeek GitHub主页的“DeepSeek实用集成”名单</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 36px;\">02&nbsp;</span></strong></span></h2>\n  <h2 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 20px;\">搜索、办公、娱乐、教育</span></strong></h2>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;color: rgb(75, 110, 245);\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 20px;\">57个App被DeepSeek重塑</span></strong></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\">还有不少官宣部署DeepSeek模型并集成至自家应用的企业，未出现在DeepSeek的名单中，智东西对这类新公布的应用进行了统计。</span></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\">据智东西统计，目前已经官宣的应用共计57个，涵盖金融、教育、医疗、办公、智能助手、娱乐购物等场景。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"3238\" data-ratio=\"5.762037037037037\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/37e9ef20-41de-4162-6a1f-7e73fc4de600/public\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/37e9ef20-41de-4162-6a1f-7e73fc4de600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">▲接入DeepSeek模型国内应用盘点（整理自公开信息，如有缺漏欢迎在评论区补充）</span></p>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: PingFangSC-Light;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\">其中，数量最多的是金融相关的企业，江苏银行、重庆银行、重庆农村商业银行以及数十家基金、证券公司已经将其应用到了投资研究、产品销售、客户服务等核心业务场景之中。</span></p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;l